title: Which chain should PSP launch on ?
body:
ParaSwap has been running on Ethereum since September 2019, it expanded to multiple chains this year and the volumes have been impressive in all 3 chains!

With the launch of ParaSwapPool staking & PSP, we'd like to kickoff the ParaSwap DAO with the very first major vote: Which chain should PSP launch on ? The ParaSwap Foundation proposes that PSP should be available in all EVM chains, so this vote will set up the first one before we roll up other chains.

To help make an educated decision, please look at this dashboard https://paraswap.io/dashboard, it shows volumes on all chains.

Discussions can happen on 
Discord: https://paraswap.io/discord
Twitter: https://twitter.com/paraswap

In Community We Trust!
